    <section name="Home Workspace">
      <span class="shortdesc">What and where is the home workspace?</span>

   <div class='screenshot'>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M13/contribs/home_workspace.png" alt='home workspace'/>      
    <p>
      The home <a href='../../contributors/concepts/workspace.html'>workspace</a>.
     </p>
   </div>

    <p>
     The home workspace is the
     <a href='../../contributors/concepts/workspace.html'>workspace</a> where you can
     work with general aspects,
     like your todo list and the history list of actions of all users.
     Requests from <a href='../../contributors/concepts/contributor.html'>contributors</a>
     will be shown in your home workspace. You can also conveniently
     <a href='../howto/handle_request.html'>handle these request</a> here.
    </p>

  <subsection name='Alternative'>
